{"tid":2038311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抛磚] 學對家搞收集簽名反國安法有冇得諗?","createTime":"2020-05-27T13:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T13:51:18.000Z","uid":148983,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"15887d41d8bd2fd78e2839b3d0bcd727ca96be12","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"近日見到好𨳍多建制擺街站, 用以下幾個方法加簽名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 1. 防疫包誘導老人家簽名支持國安法: </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200527/N2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FN2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32T2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5ade4449\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FN2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4%2F&h=15c3f292\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200527/N2OMHZLY555B4MAON2PZTTU4V4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 2. 中資逼員工簽名: </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200526/X7KUX7DQV364HBO6PTVRCALEPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200526%2FX7KUX7DQV364HBO6PTVRCALEPU%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32T2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=41f238bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200526%2FX7KUX7DQV364HBO6PTVRCALEPU%2F&h=76566f9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200526/X7KUX7DQV364HBO6PTVRCALEPU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 3. 自己𨳊簽 (話冇你都唔會信啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) </span><br />\n<br />\n咁我哋動用區議員 + 立法會議員擺街站講解之餘叫佢哋聯署, 同時叫埋黃店老闆+員工一齊聯署有冇得諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好過個別界別自己發動聯署, 數字上壯觀啲, 同時多界別一齊疊馬啲 <br />\n自行發動網上聯署小弟唔建議, 大家嚟到網上聯署之類嘅行動有時比較懶, 加上簽得嘅都只會留喺同溫層, 倒不如議員+政黨+義工追住建制擺街站咁擺效益好似更大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時間蘋果可以嘗試派狗仔隊去捕啲建制自己𨳊簽嘅證據, 然後喺我哋擺街站嘅時候貼出嚟, 進一步降低公信力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb0ce5b9eaced41831f9fb80eba1bac20350175","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f8231963d6ace8fcdd253b6b0aec210153b4a57","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72140e704e47acdae3d56d75216e6e15c1cb43e8","tid":2038311,"uid":357118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"見到有區議員做緊 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b4b5600e5b0bc4d2dc3a52376f4d6b1924505e","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"097376d8964fd47f1bd72c49b8e6dfdb492c5edb","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5c999d03b975c229e3c1fc8aff656e334b49db6","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f16b3f37586b709f89ecec17bbbbe5225c6a5395","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5253b6e5df8fe7c4f45585342acd0aa6da1d4f18","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:14:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"411b7f1750479684898e8d3ae499e635d057a7e6","tid":2038311,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae7c1592621be3f1ef48ceee4443b417a47cf90b","tid":2038311,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:15:23